            <title>[CAMEL-21807] camel-kamelet - Custom kamelet with dynamic query parameter with sql component</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-21807</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you build a custom kamelet with the sql component, then this works&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
  &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; - to:
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; uri: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;{{local-sql-postgres-sink}}:{{query}}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; parameters:
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; dataSource: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;#bean:{{dsBean}}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and this fails&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
  &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; - to:
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; uri: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;{{local-sql-postgres-sink}}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; parameters:
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; dataSource: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;#bean:{{dsBean}}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; query: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;{{query}}&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
